---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import TimeLineElement from "../components/cv/TimeLine.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Resume" sideBarActiveItemID="cv">
  <div class="mb-5">
    <div class="text-3xl w-full font-bold">Profile</div>
  </div>

  <div class="mb-10 text-justify">
    I'm M Muslim Abdul J, a passionate and
    dedicated Fullstack Web Developer currently pursuing a degree in Engineering with a major in Informatics Engineering. Proficient in Vue JS and
    Laravel, I excel at crafting immersive web experiences and dynamic user
    interfaces. Beyond my core stack, I love exploring projects using Kotlin and
    Python, offering versatility and adaptability. Engaging in personal projects
    and open-source contributions, I continuously refine my skills to create
    innovative solutions that elevate user experiences. Aiming for both academic
    excellence and practical expertise, my academic journey provides a strong
    foundation for technology's theoretical aspects. I thrive in collaborative
    environments and am open to exciting development opportunities. If you seek
    a motivated and skilled Fullstack Web Developer to bring your ideas to life,
    let's connect and embark on web development journeys together!
  </div>

